OL,6,FNHS hospitals and buildings are
OL,7,Fplagued by rats, cockroaches,
OL,8,Fsilverfish and other pests, according
OL,9,Fto a large staff survey.
OL,11,FA poll of almost 9,000 health workers
OL,12,Ffor the Unison union suggests pests
OL,13,Fmay be thriving in damp conditions and
OL,14,Funfixed buildings.
OL,16,FStaff also reported sewage leaks,
OL,17,Fdefective lighting, broken toilets and
OL,18,Fcrumbling ceilings.
