OL,3,CNHS hospitals plagued by rats,
OL,4,Ccockroaches and silverfish, staff say
OL,6,FOf those polled, around one in six
OL,7,F(16%) said they had seen vermin such
OL,8,Fas rats inside their building in the
OL,9,Fpast 12 months.
OL,11,FSimilarly, 16% said there had been
OL,12,Fother infestations such as silverfish,
OL,13,Fants and cockroaches.
OL,15,FSilverfish are metallic, silvery bugs
OL,16,Fthat thrive in damp conditions while
OL,17,Fcockroaches can carry diseases and
OL,18,Fillnesses such as gastroenteritis,
OL,19,Fdiarrhoea, typhoid and salmonella.
