OL,6,FRats carry several diseases such as
OL,7,Fleptospirosis (Weil's disease), which
OL,8,Fis spread in their urine.
OL,10,FThe new survey also found 17% of staff
OL,11,Fdo not think their building is safe.
OL,13,FMore than half (52%) reported seeing
OL,14,Fbuckets catching leaking water in
OL,15,Ftheir workplace buildings in the past
OL,16,Fyear while almost a quarter (23%)
OL,17,Fwitnessed sewage leaks.
